Enjoy the freedom of no HOA fees and the durability of brick and vinyl construction. Inside, luxury vinyl plank floors elevate the interior, while the upper-floor master provides a peaceful escape. Nestled in a setting that feels like the countryside yet conveniently close to city amenities, this property offers the best of both worlds.
